-- Mitsubishi-UFJ Plans to Increase Energy, Environment Loans, Nikkei Reports
-- B y   Y o s h i a k i   N o h a r a
-- 2010-10-10T01:07:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-10/mitsubishi-ufj-plans-to-increase-energy-environment-loans-nikkei-reports.html
Mitsubishi UFJ Financial Group Inc.
plans to advance as much as 500 billion yen ($6 billion) in low-
interest loans to energy and environment projects from next
week, the Nikkei newspaper said, without citing anyone.  To contact the reporter on this story:
